items.badge_description: We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 235 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 48!

Same great liquid, sexy new look. World-class rated Crème Brûlée imperial stout is back and more beautiful than ever. Filled with burnt crème, roasty malt and caramel sweet flavors, it’s the perfect dessert by itself AND as a beer float. Available in 22oz. bottles & 12oz four packs. More at stbcbeer.com

Get out there and raise a ruckus with your favorite Amber or Red Ale! That is 35 different beers with the style of American Amber / Red Ale, American Amber / Red Lager, Irish Red Ale or Imperial / Double Red Ale. Try 5 more for Level 8!
Load up those hops, watch the IBU grow and drink it down! Now you’re all hopped up. The more bitter, the better. That's 150 different beers with an IBU of 65 or higher. Try 5 more for Level 31!

When a single isn’t enough, make it a double. Doubling the hops and malts in a recipe results in a higher ABV and can pack quite a boozey punch. That's 20 different beers with the style that contains Imperial / Double in its style name. Try 5 more for Level 5!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 230 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 47!
Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 115 distinct venues!

You've enjoyed all that commercial beer has to offer, so now it’s time to try some home brew. Be it your friend’s or your own, it tastes better home grown. That's 4 different beers that are homebrews. Try 2 more for Level 3!
Once you’ve had just one, there’s no doubt you’ll be saying "I'll be bock" for another. That's 10 different Bock beers. Try 5 more for Level 3!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 20 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 5!
Cheers to another year of great beer! Raise a pint as we welcome 2017 and all the wonderful beer adventures it will bring!
Ahh, the trusty pale ale; crisp, refreshing, and always a good choice in a bind. That's 55 different Pale Ales. Try 5 more for Level 12.
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 225 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 46!

items.badge_description:
Das sind mindestens 25 deutsche Biere! David Hasselhoff would be proud of you. Prost!

That's 25 different German Beers! Try 5 more for Level 6.

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 65 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 14!
It’s been a long day. Time to get your drink on. You’ve had 10 beers from 5PM - 8PM on weekdays at a location in a calendar month.

The leaves are changing color, which means it's that magical time of year full of festivals, sausages, and of course, plenty of bubbly brews! Enjoy your Oktoberfest and don't forget your lederhosen. That's 15 different beers with the style of Festbier or Märzen. Try 5 more for Level 4!
